fields.name: hair_styling
fields.discription: Use a good hair wax to shape and style your hair as you want. There are different types of hair wax depending on how much setting power you want and what finish you want your hair to have. There are wax that gives matte, natural or glossy finish. For best results apply the wax warmed between your palms and directly onto towel-dried or dry hair

fields.name: shampoo
fields.discription: Wash your hair with schampoo before you use a conditioner if you have thin hair. If you have tick hair, normally it is better to use a conditioner before you use schampoo. The hair become more easy to comb afterwards. It might be good to change shampoos regularly to avoid build ups from the products.

fields.name: conditioner
fields.discription: People with thick hair can benefit from using a conditioner before they use schampoo. The hair become more easy to comb. On the other hand if you have thin hair, use a conditioner after you have uses shampoo - to get good volume.

fields.name: body_lotion
fields.discription: Combined products are practical and saves space in both your bag and your bathroom. With a Hair & Body Wash, you get a good shampoo to wash your hair clean, but you can also use it to clean your entire body. You do not need to bother with multiple bottles or tubes. Many Hair & Body Shampoos are 2-in-1 products but there are also 3-in-1, where you also get the moisturizing properties from a conditioner.

fields.name: shower_gel
fields.discription:
Treat yourself to a delightful and luxurious feeling when you shower and clean your body. Here we have gathered all the shower gels and liquid shower soaps that cleans effectively but also leaves a good scent behind. Do you want to keep the number of products to a minimum, invest in a combined Hair & Body Wash that works as a hair shampoo as well as a body soap.

A good idea is to combine deodorant, perfume and shower gel with similar fragrances. That will create a more uniform smell and you can fine tune with a matching perfume on top.

fields.name: moustache_care
fields.discription: Moustache care contains basicly three steps. Keep the moustache clean, trim and prepp the moustache. With the right tools it becomes more easy and enjoyable.

fields.name: beard_care
fields.discription: Beard care means keeping your beard clean, trimming and prepping the beard. With the right tools and products the beard care becomes more easy and fun. We are an online store that sells premium products for cutting, washing and brushing beards. All you need for growing, and styling a really nice beard.

fields.name: body_soap
fields.discription: A good body soap cleans effectively without dehydrating the skin. There are many nice solid body soaps available that you can use in the shower or bath tub when washing your body. Most of the sweat and dirt are dissolved with warm water and soap. Buy a body soap of good quality that you can rely on, that does the job effectively with only a small amount of soap.
